snippet.title: Street Fighter V: Champion Edition - Luke Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
"I'll never lose to anyone!" ⭐

Street Fighter V's final character, Luke, is fully armed to take on any opponent with his unique V-System and offense-heavy playstyle!
